properties.Name: SurveyType
properties.Description:
The classification of the type of Survey based upon Survey subjects that have common attributes, characteristics or objectives.

Ex:
-  Product satisfaction  
-  Customer needs  
-  Quality control
-  Competitor products
-  Job Satisfaction
